Description. Male. Length from thorax to the posterior end of terminalia: 4.8–5.0 mm (n= 15 ). Wing length: 3.9–4.3 mm (n= 15 ). Eyes separated by 2.3 facet diameters; frontal area with 12–21 setae alveoli (
Fig. 1
